Do Not Go Gentle Into Cognitive Science

Do not go gentle into cognitive science,
Sub 3.3 GPA should rave when it's time to declare.
Raise your fists and show your defiance,
Your voice loud, your teeth bared.
 
It's not too late to change your path,
Don't give up on homework, don't settle for less
So steer away from applied math.
Because as we all know, CS is the best.

Rage, rage against your dying GPA,
Kick and scream and shout and fight.
And as the soft embrace of dusk follows the day,
Do not go gentle into that good night.
